{"tid":983977,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】大家覺得有乜方法可以解決英國脫歐困局？","createTime":"2019-01-16T12:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T02:31:23.000Z","uid":29188,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ff96b9ab7784394aa76e5a525f7f60664722bc13","tid":983977,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"抛磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以搞二次公投<br />\n今次就有三個選項<br />\n1）May姐方案<br />\n2）No Deal Brexit<br />\n3）留歐<br />\n<br />\n但公投唔應該三揀一，而係三個options排rank<br />\n如果有一個options過半數，就採用嗰個方案<br />\n否則，就淘汰最少人為首選嗰個Option, 將所有被淘汰選票之中嘅次選撥入其餘兩個options<br />\n再睇淨低呢兩個options邊個多票<br />\n<br />\n然後再狠心啲，加多條條款，表明一旦脫歐的話，蘇格蘭同北愛將有權公投自決<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賭上成個英國國運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇吓仲有幾多堅定脫歐份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58fe953d6cde6b8b0fd0c5cd339a968121347104","tid":983977,"uid":94828,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"同香港合併<br />\n脫歐費香港俾<br />\n平過明日大嶼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b7b7c48392cec8fc33181d331df9d80bf95a57","tid":983977,"uid":47422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:11:12.000Z","msg":"當你留歐<br />\n支持脫歐人士又要搞第三次公投<br />\n根本死局"},{"pid":"2b77dd0ffb6a24d359325dda4cd177676710dca3","tid":983977,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b7b7c48392cec8fc33181d331df9d80bf95a57","tid":983977,"uid":47422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:11:12.000Z","msg":"當你留歐<br />\n支持脫歐人士又要搞第三次公投<br />\n根本死局"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T12:15:01.000Z","msg":"有埋方案你揀，終極一投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88b0a3838bea4f6e476b5abf4b2cad8ff8b3717","tid":983977,"uid":47422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q